{"tid":351915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：教育局初步查明「影子學生」投訴屬實","createTime":"2017-08-08T11:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T12:46:13.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a035c18f11ae3ddff6199c2f52e431f2ec124a2","tid":351915,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:57:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=231398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D231398&d=yJQ656Fu5PdWEkehGdisFbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=a49fe407\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D231398&h=8a32766f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=231398</a><br />\n<br />\n1小時前<br />\n【Now新聞台】消息指，教育局初步查明「影子學生」投訴屬實，教育局局長楊潤雄表示，早在二月已收到涉及興德學校的投訴，調查期間收到的投訴更多，會繼續跟進，希望不影響學生九月開學。<br />\n<br />\n興德學校被投訴製造「影子學生」，有學生全年請假沒有出現過。<br />\n<br />\n根據教育局《學校行政手冊》，若有學生連續缺課，不論學生年齡或缺席原因，校長必須於缺課第七天向教育局申報，不得延誤。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，教育局初步查明投訴屬實。<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄表示，自二月已收到涉及興德學校的投訴，之後發現學校更多問題。教育局是否監管不力，楊潤雄只重申會依程序跟進。<br />\n<br />\n教育局派員加入校董會後首次召開會議就流會收場，楊潤雄認為不能因此認定校方不合作，只希望學校的問題，不影響學生九月開學。"},{"pid":"42e87952f28bcd60305da7de5b0f31866693d7ce","tid":351915,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"執得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a995e15920ad1043e3e5e0891f18e66469239ae4","tid":351915,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd712918617a959b904cd343ff56dab52d4678c3","tid":351915,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:32:37.000Z","msg":"殺校<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80737c646907146a6eb6440a0acb94c881ed3a98","tid":351915,"uid":8048,"like":0